Happy National GF day my dearest sweetest princess! This is (one of) your day!!!! And I want you to feel very happy because you make me very happy! I hope this little gift of mine can make you feel appreciated and loved! Super love ko kase yung bby bunioncakes ko na to na super sarap ikiss paulit ulit HUHUHU 

Ang cute cute mo pa nung isang araw kase akala mo wala akong surpise sayo HAHAHAH I love you so much my bby!!! Patay na patay ako sayo kaya dapat may gift talaga ako sayo hmp!! Tapos ang hirap pa itago ng gift HAHAHAHA Nung monday ko pa kase kinuha HAHAHA. Tas napapaisip ako what if maamoy mo kase naglalast yung amoy sa room ko (naamoy mo nga HAHAHA, nung tinanong mo kung nagpabango ako AHAHHAHA). Tapos baka nakita mo pa kahapon sa gallery ko HAHAHA. Anyways!!! Happy National GF day ulit my national bby bunioncakes!! The best GF in the world! Pakak na pakak!
